### Registro de usuário
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123456",
  "password_confirm": "senha123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha123456"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refresh_token}}"
}

### Perfil do usuário
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Atualizar perfil
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva Santos",
  "email": "joao.santos@exemplo.com"
}

### Configurações do usuário
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/configuracao/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Atualizar configurações
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/users/configuracao/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tema": "escuro",
  "moeda": "BRL",
  "formato_data": "DD/MM/YYYY",
  "notificacoes_email": true
}